name: Stack site
body:
### Stack Details
handME uses 
* Python powers our backend
* Java powers our Android client.
* Objective C and swift for iOS client.
* C# for windows client.
* Postgres database.
* Nginx as http and reverse proxy server.
* Demo will be created with PhoneGap.
